A project to make a weird roguelike in Python using libtcod (roguecentral.org/doryen/libtcod)
Everyone is welcome to contribute. For the sake of preserving a modicum of sanity, this folder is a git repo, so please use commits. Branches are also welcome.

Instructions for stuff will go here when there is stuff to have instructions for:


In the meantime, check out www.roguebasin.com/index.php?title=Complete_Roguelike_Tutorial,_using_python%2Blibtcod for help on how to get started.
